I highly assure you that you will love this song and much better, love the whole CD! Los Temerarios are considered the best group not only in Mexico but world wide. I have the fortune to own every piece on music they have and all of them are wonderfull! So why hear my comments if you can prove it yourself? Go out and buy everything you find with the name of "Los Temerarios"!! Y que viva Fresnillo Zacatecas!!
